<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Satayeh</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Satayeh</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        O excursie de toata ziua catre casa delfinilor - una dintre singurele 3 locuri din lume, unde ai cea mai mare sansa sa vezi delfinii spirali in mediul lor natural
        De asemenea reciful este de tip 'potcoava de cal', fiind considerat cel mai frumos loc de snorkeling in tot Marsa Alamul. Pranzul pe barca si bauturile non alcoolice sunt incluse.
        Echipamentul de snorkeling (masca,teava,inotatoare) sunt disponibile contra cost. Vesta de salvare este obligatorie in timpul snorkelingului.
        Sosirea la hotel este în jurul orelor 17:00-17:30
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        vineri
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        A whole day sea excursion to “house of dolphins” –one of only 3 places in the world where We have a 
        highest chance to see spiral dolphin in its natural enviroment! Also the reef is a “horse shoe” type, which 
        is considered as one of the most beautifull snorekling spots in whole Marsa Alam. Lunch on the boat and 
        non alcoholic drinks included. Snorekling equipment (mask,pipe,feence) available on extra charge. Life 
        vest wearing is obligatory during snorekling!!! Arrival to hotel at 17:00-17:30.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Friday
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>